(text "MIC PERFORMANCE: DC gain 1, audio-band gain 5.99V/V; shelving pole about 34Hz; feedback pole about 27kHz." (at 20.32 698.5 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 4af07aad-dbed-5d78-9912-1a912ef67707))
(text "MIC TARGET: voice/conference capture up to about 105dBSPL. Expected analog clipping near 112-113dBSPL; this assembly is not a high-SPL recorder." (at 20.32 702.31 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid c33d1594-7f01-50c9-8976-03953c0d8ea8))
(text "MIC LAYOUT: microphone and preamp are chip-down on the main PCB. Place at a front/top acoustic opening, far from blower, class-D outputs, RF PAs, and switching inductors." (at 20.32 706.12 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid cd47f521-7390-586d-960d-ef2e217f2bd5))
(text "MIC RELEASE GATE: verify footprint/stencil with assembler, seal the acoustic path, and test clipping/noise/echo with fans, radios, speakers, USB, and charging active." (at 20.32 713.74 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 759be962-e6c9-54d5-8156-800df18bfac7))
(text "RELEASE GATES:" (at 20.32 736.6 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 799f6d47-c2f1-589f-a920-6e53db66b74e))
(text "1. Initial speakers: 8 ohm nominal and >=2W continuous each. Never join either BTL output to GND or use a shared speaker return." (at 20.32 744.22 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 0e840851-bb27-53eb-ab53-4ae04b2bbf6b))
(text "2. A 4-ohm speaker is allowed only after amplifier/PCB thermal test, excursion test, current-budget check, and enforced host volume limiting." (at 20.32 751.84 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid bf0ca4b5-cd79-5954-b357-6f10870ac6d3))
(text "3. Measure both crystal frequencies/startup margin, USB2 90-ohm routing, reset timing, and P5 enumeration on the production Mu BIOS." (at 20.32 759.46 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 97782f66-e608-5d6b-817e-9875f00916a3))
(text "4. Confirm the OS enumerates distinct PCM2900C system audio and PCM2902C radio audio devices across cold boot and suspend/resume." (at 20.32 767.08 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 8d7578cc-29e1-5325-a27f-c9b51c6ff846))
(text "5. Verify fail-off AUDIO_MIC_EN and the actual MIC_2V8-rail indicator; then run pop, echo, privacy, fan/charger noise, excursion, and RF-desense tests." (at 20.32 774.7 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 58095205-15bf-520a-8937-7c5e51c6b0f0))
(text "LAYOUT: place hub bypass/RBIAS/crystal at U400; codec crystal/decoupling at U410; mic chain at MK430; keep BTL pairs away from RF and mic input." (at 20.32 782.32 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 5bcd65cd-b3e1-5e76-8b01-9113f06f31c9))
(text "HUB_VBUS_DET follows the supervised carrier-generated physical INTERNAL_USB_VBUS. The audio hub cannot wake S3 and must re-enumerate after resume." (at 20.32 789.94 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid fbc47aa9-bb5d-5fe9-8c47-22ef90ed83ee))
